  (215, 'buckskin-shootout-main-event-champion-daniel-vallevik', 'Buckskin Shootout Main Event Champion Daniel Vallevik', 'Congratulations Buckskin Shootout Main Event Champion Daniel Vallevik from Williston ND. He defeated 56 players taking home $4200. Daniel has also secured his seat in the Tournament of Champions, and joined the race for Player of the Year.…', '2024-02-11 00:10:00', null, 'dakota-poker-tour-2023-24-buckskin-shootout-buckskin-shootout-main-event-02-10-2024', 'https://dakotapokertour.com/storage/article/thumb/IMG_0966-bjY0znXD.jpg', '/media/dpt/article/IMG_0966-bjY0znXD.jpg', null, '{"id":215,"title":"Buckskin Shootout Main Event Champion Daniel Vallevik","alias":"buckskin-shootout-main-event-champion-daniel-vallevik","excerpt":"Congratulations Buckskin Shootout Main Event Champion Daniel Vallevik from Williston ND. He defeated 56 players taking home $4200. Daniel has also secured his seat in the Tournament of Champions, and joined the race for Player of the Year.…","content":"Congratulations Buckskin Shootout Main Event Champion Daniel Vallevik from Williston ND. He defeated 56 players taking home $4200. Daniel has also secured his seat in the Tournament of Champions, and joined the race for Player of the Year. Thank you everybody who came out to support The Dakota Poker Tour, our Host Buckskin Bar and Grill, our Charity Ezra Barrows Post 46 American Legion 1st $4200 Daniel Vallevik Williston, ND 2nd $2620 Sam Fandrich Golden Valley, ND 3rd $2000 Jeff Gab Dickinson, ND 4th $1400 Wendell Vigen Killdeer, ND 5th $1150 Lorry Sirios Williston, ND 6th $950 Marcos Sotelo Star, ID 7th $750 Justin Young Bird Minot, ND 8th $600 Kevin Krohn Dickinson, ND 9th $460 Rodney Zalesky Dickinson, ND","publishedAt":"2024-02-11 00:10:00","featured":true,"logo":"IMG_0966-bjY0znXD.jpg","banner":null,"videoUrl":null,"imageUrl":"https://dakotapokertour.com/storage/article/thumb/IMG_0966-bjY0znXD.jpg","bannerUrl":"","tournament":{"id":272,"name":"Buckskin Shootout Main Eve