  (35, 'congratulations-satya-vegi-dead-money-open', 'Congratulations Satya Vegi Dead Money Open', 'Congratulations to Satya Vegi for his 1st place finish at the Dead Money Open earning $5246 and a seat into the Tournament of Champions and is in the race for Player Of The Year. 1st $5246 Satya Vegi West Fargo ND 2nd $4000 Kevin Kleinschmi…', '2022-02-13 23:00:00', null, 'dakota-poker-tour-season-xi-dead-money-open-dead-money-open-02-12-2022', 'https://dakotapokertour.com/storage/article/thumb/hL5wXdsmnYkuPeRbyCBdSJWYiN429dvRCaGpgEQb.jpg', '/media/dpt/article/hL5wXdsmnYkuPeRbyCBdSJWYiN429dvRCaGpgEQb.jpg', null, '{"id":35,"title":"Congratulations Satya Vegi Dead Money Open","alias":"congratulations-satya-vegi-dead-money-open","excerpt":"Congratulations to Satya Vegi for his 1st place finish at the Dead Money Open earning $5246 and a seat into the Tournament of Champions and is in the race for Player Of The Year. 1st $5246 Satya Vegi West Fargo ND 2nd $4000 Kevin Kleinschmi…","content":"Congratulations to Satya Vegi for his 1st place finish at the Dead Money Open earning $5246 and a seat into the Tournament of Champions and is in the race for Player Of The Year. 1st $5246 Satya Vegi West Fargo ND 2nd $4000 Kevin Kleinschmidt Crosby MN 3rd $2500 Lavan Culkins Shevlin MN 4th $2000 Michael Columbas Red Lake Falls MN 5th 1600 Brady Zimmerman Grand Forks ND 6th $1250 Chuck Bergeson Fargo ND 7th $1100 Ben Voltz Warroad MN 8th $900 Steve Belland Bagley MN 9th $700 Brad Pausch Whapeton ND 10th $550 J.W. Ogema MN￼ 11th $550 Jerrod Strode Fargo ND 12th $550 Richard Omang West Fargo ND 13th $500 Joel Smith Henning MN 14th $500 Danny Daniels Fargo ND 15th $500 Casey Smith Fargo ND 16th $450 Wade Hendrickson Cando ND 17th $450 Cade Bakke Roseau MN 18th Basim Habib Moorhead MN","publishedAt":"2022-02-13 23:00:00","featured":true,"logo":"hL5wXdsmnYkuPeRbyCBdSJWYiN429dvRCaGpgEQb.jpg","banner":"","videoUrl":null,"imageUrl":"https://dakotapokertour.com/storage/article/thumb/hL5wXdsmnYku